arStrings.szText: Hmm. A fair question. One that I myself have been wondering. I see our people struggling. I hear them talking, their faith wavering. I want to help, but...
I fear that our struggle is in part due to our faith. We refuse to learn. To adapt. You saw Maugan's Works. You saw where our faith led us.
I hope that our faith can change as I have, and we can make a home of the swamp. I don't know how, but at least for now, it means having drinks with friends.
